#2610
The Fount of Wisdom~
At this location, is a fantasticly beautiful fountain, carved of the finest
marble, a huge dragon, with it's wings spread magestically, stands in the
middle of the fountain, over fifteen spans high, from base to tip of snout,
the dragon spews forth an unmistakably magical water from it's mouth. The
water is a lovely shade of turquoise, with a hint of gold sparkle to it. At
the base of the fountain is an etched redstone plaque.
Items: Plaque.
~
