E
plaque~
The Plaque Reads:
   Know Ye this, Thou must answer my question true, or fail to receive the
gift of Wisdom. Mine question may change in form, and ye may answer as many as
ye wishith. But the true gift be known to thee the knowledge of where thy
quest should lie. The gifts I give to thee are free, only one however is
what thou seeketh, where true adventure may be found.
~
E
fountain~
The fountain looks as it is described. Quite lovely.
~
E
dragon~
Tis naught but a white dragon of marble.
~
E
water~
Yes, it's water, you can drink it.
~
E
within~
The truest answers always lie within oneself. Look deep within, to discover
what thou truly seeketh.
~
E
secret~
